text: Prez is a municipality in Saane in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2020 the municipalities Corserey, Noréaz, and Prez-vers-Noréaz joined together to become the new municipality of Prez. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2020 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Sarine
